## Kom igång

Ladda ner repot.

---

## Installera packages

# Install swagger

dotnet add package Swashbuckle.AspNetCore

# Create test project

dotnet new xunit -n CurrencyDeltaApi.Tests

# Add reference

dotnet add CurrencyDeltaApi.Tests reference CurrencyDeltaApi.csproj

# (Optional but recommended)

dotnet new sln
dotnet sln add CurrencyDeltaApi.csproj
dotnet sln add CurrencyDeltaApi.Tests/CurrencyDeltaApi.Tests.csproj

---

## Bygg och kör

dotnet clean
dotnet build
dotnet run

---

## Testa med Postman

Starta applikationen:
dotnet run

Gör en POST request till:
[https://localhost:xxxx/currencydelta](https://localhost:xxxx/currencydelta)

Sätt header:
Content-Type: application/json

Body:
{
"baseline": "GBP",
"currencies": ["USD"],
"fromDate": "2025-01-01",
"toDate": "2025-01-10"
}

---

## Kör tester

dotnet test CurrencyDeltaApi.Tests
